data.description: Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood, this well maintained- One owner, single-family home offers 2091 square feet of living space, featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The open floor plan creates a welcoming flow between the spacious living, kitchen, and dining areas, providing an ideal setting for both everyday living and entertaining guests.  The chef's eat-in kitchen is the standout feature, boasting plenty of storage and counter space. Bright and inviting, the kitchen, dining, and foyer feature  modern lighting fixtures, giving it a elegant feel.    The home has a split floor plan with a "flex" room (currently used as 5th bedroom) at the front of the home and the private Master bedroom, sitting at the back, it includes a spacious master bathroom, including double sinks and separate shower.    You will find that all 3 additional bedrooms are a perfect size for guests or families.   The backyard is secluded and private and includes a paved terrace for relaxing and sunbathing. With its prime location, this home provides easy access to nearby schools, beaches, and military bases, catering to the needs anyone seeking the laidback Florida lifestyle.
